reviewText: I was not impressed with this dvd. I purchased this one and rolie polie olie : Olie Winter Wonderland. This one only had three episodes on it and was not very long. Olie Winter Wonderland is way better and has more episodes. I would recommend buying Olie Winter Wonderland over this video. I would also not recommend buying both of them because they have the same episodes with the exception that Olie Winter Wonderland has more. If I would have know that this video had the same episodes as the other I could have avoided the trouble.
